import React from 'react';
import { AppBar, Toolbar, Button, Box } from '@mui/material';
import { Link as RouterLink } from 'react-router-dom';

function SecondaryNavbar() {
  return (
    <AppBar position="static" sx={{ backgroundColor: '#333' }}>
      <Toolbar>
        <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
          <Button color="inherit" component={RouterLink} to="/">
            Home
          </Button>
          <Button color="inherit" component={RouterLink} to="/#news">
            News
          </Button>
          <Button color="inherit" component={RouterLink} to="/#projects">
            Projects
          </Button>
          <Button color="inherit" component={RouterLink} to="/#publications">
            Publications
          </Button>
          <Button color="inherit" component={RouterLink} to="/#people">
            People
          </Button>
          <Button color="inherit" component={RouterLink} to="/#join">
            Join Us
          </Button>
        </Box>
      </Toolbar>
    </AppBar>
  );
}

export default SecondaryNavbar;
